high_descs: Pick up the banana from the shelf.
Take the banana to the microwave and open the microwave door.
Put the banana in the microwave and start the microwave.
Take the banana out of the microwave and walk to the diningtable.
Put the banana on the diningtable next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Get the banana to the microwave and then to the dining table.

high_descs: Leave the room take a left and go to the shelf on your left.
Pick up the banana on the bookshelf.
Go to the microwave behind you.
Put the banana in and turn it on then take it out.
Turn and go to the diningtable.
Put the banana next to the butcher knife on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a banana and put it on the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the room on the left and reach the shelf.
Pick up the banana from the shelf.
Turn around and reach the microwave.
Heat the banana in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and walk to the diningtable on the right.
Put the banana on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated banana on the diningtable.
